《'''羅南'''》（英語：'''{{lang|en|Ronan}}'''）是美国创作歌手[[泰勒·斯威夫特|泰勒絲]]2012年9月8日在[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]]发行的一首[[公益歌曲|公益歌曲]]。泰勒絲曾阅读马雅·汤普森的博客，博客内容与马雅2011年死于[[神经母细胞瘤|神经母细胞瘤]]的儿子罗南·汤普森（{{lang|en|Ronan Thompson}}）相关。<ref name="toc9-7-2012">{{cite web|url=http://tasteofcountry.com/taylor-swift-stand-up-to-cancer-ronan/|title=Taylor Swift to ‘Stand Up to Cancer’ With Song for 4-Year-Old Lost to Neuroblastoma|author=Megan Pacella|date=2012-09-07|work=Taste of Country|accessdate=2012-09-07|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304054321/http://tasteofcountry.com/taylor-swift-stand-up-to-cancer-ronan/|dead-url=no}}</ref>泰勒絲引用馬雅的部落格上的話，写下了这首歌並製作這首歌。2012年9月，泰勒絲在电视节目《[[对抗癌症|对抗癌症]]》首次现场表演了本歌曲。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/music-arts/taylor-swift-debut-song-ronan-stand-cancer-telethon-honor-3-year-old-victim-article-1.1154151?localLinksEnabled=false|title=Taylor Swift to debut song, 'Ronan', on 'Stand Up to Cancer' telethon in honor of 3-year-old victim|agency=Associated Press|date=2012-09-07|work=[[紐約每日新聞|New York Daily News]]|accessdate=2012-09-08|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304041759/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/music-arts/taylor-swift-debut-song-ronan-stand-cancer-telethon-honor-3-year-old-victim-article-1.1154151?localLinksEnabled=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>在此之后则只在马雅·汤普森出席的[[1989世界巡迴演唱會|1989世界巡迴演唱會]]的[[格蘭岱爾|格蘭岱爾]]站公开表演了本歌曲。<ref>{{cite web|last=Biedenharn|first=Isabella|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/08/19/taylor-swift-ronan|title=Taylor Swift sings 'Ronan' and honors woman whose son died of cancer|work=[[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2015-08-19|accessdate=2015-08-20|archive-date=2016-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160407083446/http://www.ew.com/article/2015/08/19/taylor-swift-ronan|dead-url=no}}</ref>歌曲取得的全部收入均捐献给了与抗癌相关的事业。

==背景==
泰勒絲在阅读了马雅·汤普森的博客后写下了这首歌曲。马雅是2011年一名死于[[神经母细胞瘤|神经母细胞瘤]]的儿童罗南·汤普森的母亲。<ref name="toc9-7-2012"/>马雅于2010年8月罗南被诊断患病后开始在博客{{lang|en|Rockstar Ronan}}上记录罗南与病魔抗争的全过程，直到2011年5月，罗南在他四岁生日前三天去世。在罗南去世之后，马雅仍然坚持写着博文，以此怀念罗南，并为儿童抗癌事业募款。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.songfacts.com/detail.php?id=27193 |title=Ronan by Taylor Swift Songfacts |website=Songfacts.com |date=2012-09-07 |accessdate=2016-10-17 |archive-date=2016-10-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161018223724/http://www.songfacts.com/detail.php?id=27193 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

2011年10月，泰勒絲邀请马雅观看泰勒絲在[[格蘭岱爾|格蘭岱爾]]{{tsl|en|Jobing.com Arena||Jobing.com竞技场}}的演出。泰勒絲告诉马雅自己写了一首以马雅博客内容为基础的歌曲，马雅表示，当她听到泰勒絲说“我为罗南写了一首歌”的时候，“我泪流满面，但远不止这些。她不仅为你（罗南）写了一首歌，还问我我能在国家电视网表演它吗。”<ref name="Hey Maya, it's Taylor Swift">{{cite web|url=http://rockstarronan.com/2012/09/09/hey-maya-its-taylor-swift|title=Hey Maya, it's Taylor Swift...|website=Rockstaronan.com|accessdate=2016-10-17|archive-date=2016-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161011105352/https://rockstarronan.com/2012/09/09/hey-maya-its-taylor-swift/|dead-url=no}}</ref>泰勒絲将马雅列为歌曲的创作人之一，之后在美国[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]]发行了歌曲，并在不久后于《[[对抗癌症|对抗癌症]]》现场表演了歌曲。歌曲取得的全部收入均捐献给了与抗癌相关的事业。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://music.msn.com/music/article.aspx?news=755896&GT1=28102|title=Taylor Swift to debut song for cancer victim|date=2012-09-07|work=[[MSN|MSN]]|publisher=[[微软|Microsoft]]|accessdate=2012-09-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213223821/http://music.msn.com/music/article.aspx?news=755896&GT1=28102|archive-date=2013-12-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==词曲==

编曲上，《{{lang|zh|羅南}}》主要被认为是一首[[乡村音乐|乡村]]歌曲。<ref name="iTunes">{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/ronan-single/id560227510|title=Ronan – Single|date=2012-09-08|work=[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]]|access-date=2017-02-26|archive-date=2012-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120909173236/http://itunes.apple.com/us/album/ronan-single/id560227510|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="AllMusic">{{cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/ronan-mw0002421885|title=Ronan – Taylor Swift|work=[[Allmusic|Allmusic]]|accessdate=2015-05-27|archive-date=2012-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120921103009/http://www.allmusic.com/album/ronan-mw0002421885|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Entertainment Weekly">{{cite web|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2012/09/10/taylor-swift-ronan|title=New Taylor Swift song 'Ronan': Hear her tribute to a young cancer victim|work=[[娱乐周刊|Entertainment Weekly]]|first=Grady|last=Smith|date=2012-09-10|access-date=2017-02-26|archive-date=2020-11-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201104092540/https://ew.com/article/2012/09/10/taylor-swift-ronan/|dead-url=no}}</ref>而《[[Spin_(杂志)|Spin]]》的馬克·赫根则认为《{{lang|Zh|羅南}}》是[[軟式搖滾|軟搖滾]]歌曲。<ref name="Spin">{{cite web|url=http://www.spin.com/2012/09/taylor-swift-debuts-ronan-at-cancer-benefit/|title=Taylor Swift Debuts Tear-Jerking ‘Ronan’ at Cancer Benefit|publisher=[[Spin_(杂志)|Spin]]|quote=Swift's soft-rock ballad "Ronan," inspired by a Phoenix mother's heartfelt blog post ...|first=Mark|last=Hogan|date=2012-09-10|access-date=2017-02-26|archive-date=2015-05-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150527122956/http://www.spin.com/2012/09/taylor-swift-debuts-ronan-at-cancer-benefit/|dead-url=no}}</ref>歌曲由泰勒絲創作及製作，她在創作時引用馬雅·湯普森的部落格上的話。<ref name="Hey Maya, it's Taylor Swift"/>

==乐评==
《{{lang|Zh|羅南}}》收获了乐评的好评。《[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石]]》表示歌曲“让人心碎”。<ref name="rolling">{{cite web|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/videos/taylor-swift-debuts-ronan-at-stand-up-to-cancer-benefit-20120908|title=Taylor Swift Debuts 'Ronan' at Stand Up To Cancer Benefit|date=2012-09-08|work=[[滾石_(雜誌)|Rolling Stone]]|accessdate=2012-09-09|archive-date=2016-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305071046/http://www.rollingstone.com/music/videos/taylor-swift-debuts-ronan-at-stand-up-to-cancer-benefit-20120908|dead-url=no}}</ref>{{lang|en|Taste of Country}}的比尔·杜克写道：“很明显（泰勒絲）正说出了马雅·汤普森的声音……”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://tasteofcountry.com/taylor-swifts-ronan-tim-mcgraw-stand-up-2-cancer/|title=Taylor Swift's ‘Ronan,’ Tim McGraw's ‘Live Like You Were Dying’ Highlight Emotional ‘Stand Up to Cancer’ Telethon|author=Billy Dukes|date=2012-09-07|work=Taste of Country|accessdate=2012-09-09|archive-date=2017-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171108210247/http://tasteofcountry.com/taylor-swifts-ronan-tim-mcgraw-stand-up-2-cancer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>《{{tsl|en|The Arizona Republic|亚利桑那共和报}}》的艾德·马斯里认为“《{{lang|zh|羅南}}》也许是（泰勒絲）作为一名艺人的最佳时刻。”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.azcentral.com/thingstodo/music/articles/2012/09/09/20120909taylor-swift-song-ronan-phoenix-boy-stand-up-to-cancer.html|title=Taylor Swift song 'Ronan' for Phoenix boy an artistic high|author=Ed Masley|date=2012-09-09|work=The Republic|publisher=AZ Central|accessdate=2012-09-09}}</ref>

